                <h1>How to Set Live Wallpapers on Your iPhone</h1>
                <p>Yes, you can have a live wallpaper on your iPhone! Live wallpapers are dynamic backgrounds that animate when you press down on the screen. To set one, head to Settings > Wallpaper > Choose a New Wallpaper, and then select Live. Just ensure your iPhone model supports this feature, as it's available on iPhone 6s and later.</p>
